Call recorder is a must-have app for saving every detail of your business and private calls with an intuitive and user-friendly interface. Ever forgot dates, names, numbers, or places that were mentioned during the call? It is easy to turn your phone conversations into handy voice notes for later use. Record, save and listen to phone calls anywhere and anytime in a few clicks!

Our app is an effective and easy-to-use application with its own identity by design which can help to make your life easier.
Moreover, we provide our high-quality service globally by adding service numbers that will support 9 countries (USA, UK, Germany, Japan, Brazil, Portugal, Turkey, Italy and Spain).

THE MAIN FEATURES OF OUR iPHONE CALL-RECORDING APP:
• Highly intuitive interface;
• Call Reminder Feature: Don’t forget to call someone important;
• Use “How it works” page with guides for your comfort;
• Easily add the contacts you need and start recording;
• Record incoming & outgoing calls in a few taps;
• Enjoy high-quality recordings;
• Convert voice recordings into text memos with the “speech to text” feature;
• Record local and cross-border calls;
• Access recordings as soon as the conversation is over;
• Manage your records, search and find them with ease;
• Unlimited call recording is available;
• Stay safe & private.
Do you have difficulties with foreign languages? Stay with us, we are preparing something interesting for you.

UPCOMING UPDATES:
• You will be able to translate recordings into many different languages and become even more efficient.

